member.name: T:SpreadsheetTester.SpreadsheetTester
member.summary: This tester class holds all the tests for public/protected methods of the Spreadsheet class. Extends Spreadsheet class specially for test methods that test it's protected methods. This tester class provides reasonably close to 100% code coverage.
